Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.79,0:01:42.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going through Reiko's belongings?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:46.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.19,0:01:53.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Like always, I just don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.33,0:01:55.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.00,0:01:58.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,On the sides of your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:01:59.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about them, they're just there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:07.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When I return the names back to the Youkai,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko-san's memories become my own thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and flow into me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:16.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And little by little, Reiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.28,0:02:29.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a book borrowed from the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:31.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she forgot to return it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.66,0:02:35.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:51.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy says that he eats the kitsune first in kitsune udon! {fuck yea kitsune is delicious, I do the same thing}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you should eat it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:00.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The kitsune must be put at the bottom of the soup and eaten last!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:04.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:08.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You should eat the kitsune before it absorbs the soup! {fuckin agreed man}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I think that either way is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:15.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The kitsune must be eaten later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:18.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:22.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, before arguing any more, I don't think it should be called "kitsune."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,First!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:32.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're through!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:40.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a silly fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:43.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. You dropped this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an old ticket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:47.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:52.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:55.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have some kind of history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked it up on my way to school this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're terrible at telling lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:07.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for all the details later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:16.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I wasn't running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:24.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:27.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the station on that ticket, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.08,0:04:28.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the station, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.48,0:04:32.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't see it well earlier, so I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it close?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:36.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to go so much, Sasada?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:45.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! After that test of courage the other day, I've wanted to see a real one up close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:45.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:48.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See what? Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look, the bus is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:54.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you dropped something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:57.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I drop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing was dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:07.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Look harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:10.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:21.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:25.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are {\i1}you {\i0}saying that I droppe-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here. You're late, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:50.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.03,0:05:58.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This place isn't being used anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:05:59.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:02.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that it was abandoned quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:05.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a desolate place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.39,0:06:06.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:08.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Kiriganuma is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, why did Reiko-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A Youkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he sleep in this heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Reiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:36.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Reiko! You finally came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:40.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.05,0:06:41.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:50.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:53.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to say anything to him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not evil, so just play with him a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.96,0:07:15.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So Reiko died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's her grandson, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange about them having the same smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to smell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:30.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So, furball, you said you were waiting for Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a promise with her or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:36.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she said she'd go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriganuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:47.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko-san was supposed to go with you to Kiriganuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:50.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kiriganuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:51.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:56.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Mikuri was all pouting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:58.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and said, "I can't forgive you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:03.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Reiko said, "No," and "Later."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's impossible to have him explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably in the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:14.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you return his name, I'm sure the thoughts will explain it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:17.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:19.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:20.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One who would protect me, show your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So you had a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:45.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:48.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri was the one who got angry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:51.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And you like that Youkai Mikuri, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.16,0:08:55.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:58.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mikuri said that he hates me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and that he doesn't want to see me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:04.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:08.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:14.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is Mikuri so angry with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:23.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of understand why Mikuri is angry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.78,0:09:28.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,At Kiriganuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiriganuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The place by the next station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:41.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:46.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is already setting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:48.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's meet here again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:55.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.66,0:09:57.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Santo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:05.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But she couldn't keep her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:10.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there was some reason why she couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He might not be waiting anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't know unless we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do what Reiko-san left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun is already setting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come by after school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:45.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:50.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot, making promises without thinking things through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.72,0:10:53.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any buses that pass by Kiriganuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:57.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you think it'll take to walk there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:00.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun will set by then for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there's no point in persuading you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:26.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:30.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If Reiko couldn't come, couldn't you have gone by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you wait all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I made a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was an idiot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting chilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:53.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain winds are coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:11:59.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:10.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, these kinds of people can be seen as charming or annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:16.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to say when you see Mikuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:23.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You haven't thought about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:29.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to make up, you have to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.72,0:12:37.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's better if they don't meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:41.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It might just be troublesome once he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:44.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Think of something to say before we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:51.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:51.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:55.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:56.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Malice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:10.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:15.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unforgivable! Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:17.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.74,0:13:29.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:35.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.04,0:13:36.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It was after Santo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:37.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri seems to be possessed by the earth spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,By the earth spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They feed off of anger and hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Mikuri hate Santo that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be safer if we don't go and see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:05.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:09.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Nyanko-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:30.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like it's not even summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:34.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the mountain winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because of the malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri! Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:44.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:52.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo, what does Mikuri look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.86,0:14:54.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's small.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:57.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Small?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:08.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he that small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:18.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,About that small?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be joking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's here, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:35.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.46,0:15:45.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:58.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A catfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.72,0:16:01.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Mikuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:04.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.92,0:16:07.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:17.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:35.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Natsume Reiko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.24,0:16:39.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:44.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, the Book of Friends is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Reiko's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:17:00.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri! It's me! Santo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.22,0:17:04.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Please, come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.98,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back, Mikuri! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:09.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the Book of Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:14.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:15.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:43.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:47.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:49.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:50.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:53.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mikuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:59.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad, but he disappeared along with the earth spirits to the bottom of the swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:12.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:15.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Santo! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.57,0:18:17.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing, you idiot!? Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:23.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is creepy, so let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I said let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You had a fight because of Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:38.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Natsume Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,His name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:46.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave his precious name to Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any pride as an Ayakashi, you big fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to see your face again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.52,0:18:56.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you just show up like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You useless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.91,0:18:59.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you don't have to say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:06.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been worrying about it the entire time because he likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to apologize, then get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:13.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mikuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening, furball?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:22.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:28.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They already made up a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.09,0:19:32.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikuri, let's go back to the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd go back even if you didn't tell me to, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.81,0:19:41.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! Don't bow your head to a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But he returned my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:45.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to lower your head, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Just going through it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just putting it back to where it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:10.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You said Reiko couldn't keep her promise because she had some special reason, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.47,0:20:12.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're giving her too much credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.16,0:20:15.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She just forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.54,0:20:17.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of person she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's there because she forgot to return it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:35.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it looks like she forgot quite a few things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.32,0:20:38.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have had some {\i1}really {\i0}special reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:41.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:51.26,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have a look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,They made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What was up with yesterday, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.21,0:21:00.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.59,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be because they're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.02,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How was it yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I remember now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, take this for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:22.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasada.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.19,0:21:25.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you eat the shrimp in tempura noodles first or last?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:26.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Which?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter which!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.05,0:21:36.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:38.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You looked troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.40,0:23:37.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A village submerged by a dam shows itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:41.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Youkai that live there come to have their names returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.40,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all of you! Don't hang on to Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:47.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be troubling you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.80,0:23:49.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you want to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:53.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,
